WEBVTT

00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:16.000
I saved you

00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:19.000
and I'm here to save you again.

00:00:19.000 --> 00:00:23.000
The parasites are merely a symptom of a greater sickness

00:00:23.000 --> 00:00:25.000
in Faerûn

00:00:25.000 --> 00:00:28.000
The infected hear the voice of the Absolute

00:00:28.000 --> 00:00:31.000
and believe it to be a god.

00:00:31.000 --> 00:00:39.000
The Absolute is more dangerous than you can possibly conceive

00:00:39.000 --> 00:00:42.000
It threatens all who live

00:00:42.000 --> 00:00:45.000
It threatens the gods

00:00:45.000 --> 00:00:47.000
The Weave

00:00:47.000 --> 00:00:52.000
the very fabric of the universe itself

00:00:52.000 --> 00:01:00.000
How would you feel about helping me kill some evil bastards?

00:01:00.000 --> 00:01:03.000
Vlaakith blesses me this day!

00:01:03.000 --> 00:01:06.000
Together we might survive

00:01:06.000 --> 00:01:10.000
I'll enjoy watching you try

00:01:10.000 --> 00:01:14.000
In mere moments all that you have dreaded

00:01:14.000 --> 00:01:16.000
will come to pass

00:01:16.000 --> 00:01:18.000
When the screaming stops

00:01:18.000 --> 00:01:20.000
and your mind is gone

00:01:20.000 --> 00:01:23.000
the rest perhaps

00:01:23.000 --> 00:01:28.000
is silence